---
config:
  theme: default
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant client as Client (FastAPI caller)
    participant stream as StreamingVAD (state machine)
    participant silero as SileroVAD (speech probability model)
    participant logic as DynamicEndpointDetector (decision logic)
    participant smart as AsyncSmartTurnDetector (semantic completeness)

    client->>+stream: process_chunk(audio_bytes)
    stream->>stream: 累積 buffer，滿 512 samples 才進入推論

    loop 每個 32ms chunk
        stream->>+silero: prob(chunk_f32)
        silero-->>-stream: speech probability P

        alt P > VAD_THRESHOLD
            stream->>logic: 標記 speech，重置 trailing silence (靜音)
        else P <= VAD_THRESHOLD
            stream->>logic: 累加 trailing silence
        end

        opt 達到 EARLY_CHECK_MS (例如 1.5s 靜音)
            stream->>+smart: submit_async(預留的前置音訊)
            smart-->>-stream: 背景推論中 (非同步)
        end

        stream->>smart: get_result_if_ready()
        opt 推論結果可用
            smart-->>stream: probability (P_turn/語意完整度)
            stream->>logic: on_check_completed(P_turn)
        end

        alt should_force_end(超過最大耐心容忍度) 或 should_end_by_confidence(語意非常完整)
            stream->>stream: _reset_state()
            stream-->>client: 回傳 True (觸發 ASR commit 與句點)
        else 尚未達結束條件
            stream-->>client: 回傳 False (繼續收音)
        end
    end